column2:
"I don't know why, but I had a bad
feeling something might happen. To you.
I just needed to see you."

"Oh, here you are! Matoi, you really shouldn't
go wandering around like that!"
"I'm fine. My head... just hurts a little."

"Be that as it may, you're still my patient,
and I say you need your rest. Now come
along, let's get you home."

"なんだろう、イヤな予感がしてて
会いたいなって思ってたから……"

"ああ、こんなところに！
ダメですよ、マトイちゃん
勝手に出歩いちゃ！"

"ダメです。
調子が悪いのは事実なんですから
さ、帰りますよ。"
